subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The project aims at supporting Georgia in research, analysis, elaboration and publishing of a National Human Development Report. The project is seen as the beginning of a longer process which aims at establishment of the ideology of Sustainable Human Development, promoting participatory approaches, building partnerships between the state and civil society and stimulating public debate.
subproject.title: Human Development Report
